# 🎈 Balloon Festival

## Overview

Balloon Festival is the first mini game of the Roblox Buddy AI Anniversary Event.

It is a fun, relaxing, family-friendly multiplayer game where players collect colorful balloons, complete balloon missions, help Buddy prepare the birthday celebration, and earn Anniversary rewards.

Unlike Cake Defense or Funny Battle Simulator, Balloon Festival focuses on exploration, teamwork, collecting, and celebration.

---

# 👥 Player Limit

- Solo
- 2–10 Players

Players can play alone or together.

---

# 📖 Story

Buddy wants to decorate the biggest birthday party ever.

Unfortunately...

The balloons have been scattered across the entire map.

Players must help Buddy collect every balloon before the party begins.

---

# 🎯 Objective

Players must:

- 🎈 Find balloons
- 🎈 Collect balloons
- 🎈 Complete balloon missions
- 🎈 Help decorate the Birthday Hall
- 🎁 Earn Balloon Currency

